@N0257:  ephemeral args used for passing parameters
@N0261:  loop counter
@N0263:  save the return address
@N0265:  initialize vector gen; Y offset in ACC
@N0267:  shift from 0-15 axis to -8 to +7
@N0271:  re-fetch the next x_arg
